%N A108210 Let M[n] be the 2 X 2 matrix {{0, -3}, {(n - 1), 5*(n - 1)}} and let v[1] = {0, 1}', v[n] = M[n]*v[n - 1]'. Then a[n] is the first entry of v[n].
%C A108210 Derangement-type quadratic Markov chain.
%t A108210 M[n_] := {{0, -3}, {(n - 1), 5*(n - 1)}} v[1] = {0, 1} v[n_] := v[n] = M[n].v[n - 1] a = Table[Abs[v[n][[1]]], {n, 1, 25}]
